{"tid":1877252,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"firstrade debt card 每月有一次補貼?","createTime":"2020-02-13T02:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T14:56:59.000Z","uid":89225,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3846d5a44eec553b4dd14d8a2b50884857226e9c","tid":1877252,"uid":89225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:07:39.000Z","msg":"有無巴打收到呢個email?姐係一個月提到USD 1000唔洗手續費, 好過無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nStarting today, we&rsquo;ve added a new benefit to your Cash Management Account (CMA).<br />\n<br />\nHere&rsquo;s how it works:<br />\n<br />\nTo be eligible, you must maintain a minimum account equity of $10,000 or more in your CMA.<br />\nYou will receive a refund for the first foreign transaction fee (3%) incurred each month on debit card withdrawals or purchases made outside of the U.S.<br />\nThe reimbursement will appear in your account within three business days.<br />\nAs always, we will continue to offer CMAs without an annual or maintenance fee.<br />\n<br />\nAt Firstrade, we stand by our core values everyday&mdash; commission-free investing and an ongoing commitment to excellence. We hope you enjoy your experience at Firstrade and wish to serve you for many years to come."},{"pid":"c66029b2cb8290e81e16738005c9bfe144b1a25e","tid":1877252,"uid":133200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T03:58:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ozNaH8X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FozNaH8X.png&h=a48e7d40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba172158420a3aaff179a6b715b522c6f5a009f8","tid":1877252,"uid":175194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T05:12:47.000Z","msg":"即係唔洗匯錢番來"},{"pid":"9c05bcdf9b4261b1058acd3f742c320940b96db1","tid":1877252,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T05:16:35.000Z","msg":"每個月僅限一次"},{"pid":"6247d59196c09a22ba73